overview: A companion piece to Andrew and Eden Kötting’s FORGOTTEN THE QUEEN except this time we are sailing into a male storm, a place of make believe and disaster where dog eats dog. This world is teeming with hidden dangers, orchestrated by voodoo, pooh, men in frocks and dogs. Yet many a man is making friends with death, even as we speak, because it proves to be a lot easier than logic. So, let the scatological begin….
title: Dog Ate Dog
